\section{Literal Blocks%
  \label{literal-blocks}%
}

Literal blocks are indented, and indicated with a double-colon (\textquotedbl{}::\textquotedbl{})
at the end of the preceding paragraph (right here \texttt{-{}->}):
%
\begin{quote}{\ttfamily \raggedright \noindent
if~literal\_block:\\
~~~~text~=~'is~left~as-is'\\
~~~~spaces\_and\_linebreaks~=~'are~preserved'\\
~~~~markup\_processing~=~None
}
\end{quote}

